         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Nov. 9 /81. ¶ My dear Baron ¶  ¶ I am delighted to tell you that Prof Caruel is misinformed about Mr Bentham, who is alive &amp; as well &amp; active as ever — His memory as clear &amp; mind as judicious. ¶  ¶ He...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">81.11.09</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From Joseph Hooker</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">RB MSS M3, Library, Royal Botanic Gardens Melbourne.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>MS embossed with crest of Royal Gardens Kew.</p>
               </note>Nov. 9 /81.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">My dear Baron</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I am delighted to tell you that Prof Caruel is misinformed about Mr Bentham, who is alive &amp; as well &amp; active as ever — His memory as clear &amp; mind as judicious.<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>See M to J. Hooker, 19 September 1881 (in this edition as 81-01-19a).</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>He works as steadily as ever at the Herbarium from 10 till 4 &amp; has just read at the Linnean his splendid paper on the classification of <name key="Gramineae">Gramineae</name>.<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Bentham (1882).</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>He has just concluded <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">Bromeliaceae</hi>
               </seg> for Gen. Plant.<note xml:id="ftn4" type="footnote" n="4">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Bentham &amp; Hooker (1862–83).</p>
               </note> — &amp; there is now little more than <name key="Amaryllideae">Amaryllideae</name> &amp; <name key="Liliaceae">Liliaceae</name> to do. I am finishing the Palms, leaving the Australians in I fear a disgraceful state. I have undertaken the <name key="Aroideae">Aroideae</name> &amp; when that is done I hope Gen. Plant will be concluded.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">Very sincerely yr</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Jos. D. Hooker</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
